## Interface: 120005, 50503, 20505, 11508, 120007
## Title: Cairn-Media-Browser
## Notes: Live, browseable view of every asset registered with Cairn-Media-1.0. /cmb opens a tabbed window with one tab per media type (Fonts, Statusbars, Borders, Backgrounds, Sounds) plus an Icons tab that grids the Material Symbols glyph registry. Companion to Cairn-Demo.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 1
## Dependencies: Cairn
## X-Category: Development Tools
## X-License: MIT
## DefaultState: enabled
## LoadOnDemand: 0

# Core: init, slash command, root Window + TabGroup shell. Each Tabs/*.lua
# below builds out one tab against the shared shell. Mirrors the
# Cairn-Demo / Cairn-Gui-Demo-2.0 architecture exactly.
Core.lua

# Tabs (load after Core since they call Browser:RegisterTab on it).
Tabs\Welcome.lua
Tabs\Fonts.lua
Tabs\Statusbars.lua
Tabs\Borders.lua
Tabs\Backgrounds.lua
Tabs\Sounds.lua
Tabs\Icons.lua
